    title: 'TSA 3-1-1 Liquids Rule — Complete 2026 Guide (With Exceptions)',
    excerpt: 'The 3-1-1 rule trips up even experienced travelers. Here\'s exactly what it means, what\'s allowed, and what the TSA agents actually check for.',
    category: 'Airport Security',
